                    <description><![CDATA[<p>The Workshop is <strong>free</strong>, but registration is required.</p>
<p>To register your interest in participating, please complete this form,
or send an email to Niall (<a href="mailto:Niall.Madden@UniversityOfGalway.ie">Niall.Madden@UniversityOfGalway.ie</a>) with
your name and affiliation, and information on if you wish to give a
talk.</p>
<p>The deadline for registration will be posted here 6 months before the
workshop.</p>
<p>Tea and coffee will be provided during breaks. Lunch, the conference
dinner, travel, accommodation, etc., are at the participants'
expense.</p>
]]></description>
                

